Package com.fdmgroup.MattBadmintonMatchmaker.model

Class Game

java.lang.Object
com.fdmgroup.MattBadmintonMatchmaker.model.Game
@Entity public class Game extends Object
This entity holds game information. Each game is composed of four player entities who participated in the game and among which should be two who are the winners. Input validation is done on client side to minimize backend load.
